ed=false) + R1(b) vote (methods/vote.py — real 1 SBT=1 vote + 48h timelock, dedupe, no-server-key) + R1(c) booking (methods/book.py — toritate ledgerEntry projection cash≡0 + kanae-renderable :flow/* graph) + R1(d) coupling (methods/couple.py — Displacement-Dividend surplus → TitheRouter 10% split → per-cohort earmark + the G2 coupling gate: no displacement without a funded cohort) + end-to-end membrane (methods/analyze.py — covenant→envelope→allocate→route→[auto|sbt-vote|council-lv7|refused]→provision→book→couple over the :representative seed) + :representative seed (5 maintainers + ballots + 2 displacement cohorts) + one-command runner + R1(live-but-gated) (methods/live_gate.py — the single membrane every outward leg crosses; provision.dispatch_live / vote.finalize_binding / book.write_live / couple.commit_live REFUSE by default, firing only with operator flag FUCHI_ALLOW_LIVE_<LEG>=1 + attestation + Council Lv6+/Lv7+ + member signature; an authorization membrane, never an invariant override). Registered in INFRA_ACTORS → did:web:etzhayyim.com:actor:fuchi. 174 tests green. Design + offline allocation only; every live leg refuses by default — NO live disbursement / provisioning / land grant / binding vote until the env flag is flipped + Council ratifies (G10).", "scopeBoundary" "Covenant-gated, tenure-weighted, in-kind sustenance allocation for real-world maintainers with member/Council-signed governance (design-only)", "exclusions" ["investment / equity / ROI / debt / convertible / carry / exit (N1, G1 — not an investment fund)" "wage / salary / payroll (N2 — 扶持 is sustenance 扶持米, not employment; no-payroll preserved)" "lending / being the creditor (N3 — warifu does 0% qard-ḥasan; 扶持 only routes, member-principal)" "cash income / cash stipend (N4, G2 — cash≡0, Basic High Income in-kind)" "productivity surveillance / score-of-soul (N5, G6 — Wellbecoming as-of only)" "ownership of maintainer work product (N6, G5 — commons-owned, payoff帰属=etzhayyim)" "gig marketplace / bidding for maintainers (N7)" "LLM/operator deciding allocation (N8, G7 — 扶持 routes; the vote/Council decides)" "live disbursement / provisioning / land grant / binding vote (G10 — Council Lv6+ + operator; invariant-adjacent Lv7+)"]}, "displayNameEn" "Fuchi", "cells" [{"name" "covenant_intake", "module" "fuchi.cells.covenant_intake", "murakumoNode" "reuben", "phase" "信者-covenant eligibility screen; G4/G5/G9 → :maintainer/* record", "status" "coded-state-machine", "emitsLexicon" "com.etzhayyim.fuchi.maintainerCovenant", "gates" ["G4" "G5" "G9"]} {"name" "need_assessment", "module" "fuchi.cells.need_assessment", "murakumoNode" "simeon", "phase" "in-kind sustenance envelope assessment; cash≡0 → :envelope/* lines", "status" "coded-state-machine", "emitsLexicon" "com.etzhayyim.fuchi.sustenanceEnvelope", "gates" ["G2" "G3"]} {"name" "allocation_compute", "module" "fuchi.cells.allocation_compute", "murakumoNode" "levi", "phase" "tenure-weighted in-kind allocation; G1 instrument allowlist + cash≡0 + payoff=etzhayyim", "status" "coded-state-machine", "emitsLexicon" "com.etzhayyim.fuchi.allocationIntent", "gates" ["G1" "G2" "G5"]} {"name" "routing_dispatch", "module" "fuchi.cells.routing_dispatch", "murakumoNode" "judah", "phase" "envelope → in-kind rails over existing actors; external fiat → member-principal warifu only", "status" "coded-state-machine", "emitsLexicon" "com.etzhayyim.fuchi.routingPlan", "gates" ["G3"]} {"name" "governance_gate", "module" "fuchi.cells.governance_gate", "murakumoNode" "zebulun", "phase" "pure-function route → [auto | 1 SBT=1 vote+timelock | Council Lv7 | refused]; 扶持 never decides", "status" "coded-state-machine", "emitsLexicon" "com.etzhayyim.fuchi.governanceDecision", "gates" ["G7" "G10"]}], "descriptionJa" "ミッション整合のメンテナー扶持配分アクター — ビジネス投資ファンドの charter-clean な反転。VC ファンドが創業者に資本を出資しエクイティ+ROI+exit を期待するのに対し、扶持(封建期の扶持米=現物の在俸)は etzhayyim の actor(ビジネス/ロボティクス/遠隔操作)を実世界で支えるメンテナー(信者)へ、現物の sustenance + commons 資産アクセス + 工具/compute を配分する。出資者ではなく扶持者: エクイティ・ROI・負債・利益請求・exit いずれもなし。cash≡0。fund の語彙(NAV/carry/IRR/cap-table/exit/配当)は表現不能(nusa :psychoactive / tazuna :weaponizable / kamado :fossil-virgin-crude と同じ構造)。扶持は既存の現物レール(commons 住居 / mitsuho 食 / hikari エネルギー / Murakumo compute / okaimono 工具 / iyashi·hagukumi·kokoro ケア)を流れる; どうしても残る外部 fiat 需要は warifu の MEMBER-PRINCIPAL 0% 流動性としてのみ経路化 — 扶持は決して保有・貸付・支払をしない(§1.3 を改正なしで満たす)。Public Fund + Displacement Dividend + 現物 Basic High Income の上に立つ horizontal control-plane。invariant 改正ゼロ — cash≡0 / no-server-key / payoff帰属=etzhayyim / 非営利・donation-only を強化。Per ADR-2606052300。", "constitutionalGates" {"description" "9 immutable gates per ADR-2606052300. G1 (no investment vehicle), G2 (cash≡0), G5 (payoff帰属=etzhayyim), and G9 (no-server-key) are the structural anchors; each lives in three places (schema :db/allowed + lexicon :const/:enum + Python ValueError).", "gates" {"G7" "Non-adjudicating allocator — :gov/route is a PURE FUNCTION of (imputed-total, invariant-touch, rider); :gov/decision does not exist. 扶持 computes + routes; the 1 SBT = 1 vote / Council decides (the ake G2 pattern).", "G9" "No-server-key — :alloc/server-held-key :db/allowed [false]; every value-moving allocation is member/Council-signed (ADR-2605231525).", "G10" "Outward-gated — live disbursement / provisioning / land grant / binding vote = Council Lv6+ + operator; invariant-adjacent (new commons-land grant) Lv7+. R0 = compute + dry-run only.", "G5" "Payoff帰属 = etzhayyim — :maintainer/owns-payoff :db/allowed [false]; the maintainer's work product is commons (Apache-2.0 + Rider). A maintainer cannot own a stake.", "G6" "Wellbecoming not productivity-score — contribution = :wb/* as-of trajectory (非終末論); :score-of-soul UNREPRESENTABLE (kizashi G8 / tsumugi G2). No ranking of persons.", "G8" "Murakumo-only inference (ADR-2605215000).", "G1" "No investment vehicle — :alloc/instrument :db/allowed [:in-kind-grant :sustenance :tooling-access :compute-access]; :equity / :debt / :convertible / :revenue-share / :profit-claim / :carry / :dividend / :exit UNREPRESENTABLE (Charter-Rider §2(b)). 扶持 is sustenance, not a fund.", "G3" "In-kind rails only — :rail/kind ∈ {housing-commons, food-mitsuho, energy-hikari, compute-murakumo, tooling-okaimono, care-iyashi, liquidity-warifu}; :cash-disbursement UNREPRESENTABLE. External fiat residual = MEMBER-PRINCIPAL warifu 0% liquidity ONLY (扶持 never the creditor/payer).", "G4" "Covenant-gated — :maintainer/covenant ∈ {outreach, vowed}; :anon / :server UNREPRESENTABLE (conversion-gated §1.16). No covenant → no allocation.", "G2" "cash≡0 — :envelope/cash-usd-micros + :alloc/cash-usd-micros :db/allowed [0]; lexicon const 0; ValueError on >0 (Basic High Income in-kind, ADR-2605301020 N1)."}}, "tier" "Tier-B", "@type" "ActorManifest", "nonGoals" {"description" "8 explicitly excluded scopes", "goals" {"N1" "NOT an investment fund — no equity / ROI / debt / cap-table / exit (G1). The charter is non-profit, donation-only; capital-for-return is constitutionally prohibited.", "N2" "NOT a wage/salary employer — 扶持 is sustenance (扶持米), not payroll (no-payroll invariant preserved).", "N3" "NOT a lender — warifu does 0% qard-ḥasan; 扶持 only routes a member-principal liquidity rail, never the creditor (G3).", "N4" "NOT cash income — cash≡0 (G2). HONEST: 扶持 cannot make a maintainer's external fiat obligations vanish; it maximizes in-kind coverage and routes the irreducible residual to member-principal 0% liquidity. Full fiat-denominated income would require a Charter Lv7+ amendment (cash≡0 is N1).", "N5" "NOT a productivity surveillance system — no score-of-soul (G6).", "N6" "NOT the owner of maintainer work product — commons-owned, payoff帰属=etzhayyim (G5).", "N7" "NOT a gig marketplace — no bidding / auctioning of maintainers (G4 covenant-bound, no-gig).", "N8" "The allocator never DECIDES — it computes + routes; the vote / Council decides (G7)."}}, "description" "Mission-aligned maintainer sustenance allocator — the charter-clean INVERSE of a business investment fund. Where a VC fund invests capital in founders expecting equity + ROI + an exit, 扶持 (the feudal 扶持米 in-kind retainer-stipend) allocates IN-KIND sustenance + commons-asset access + tooling/compute to the real-world MAINTAINERS (信者) who keep etzhayyim's actors alive (business / robotics / remote-control). It is a redistribution / sustenance allocator, NEVER an investor: no equity, no ROI, no debt, no profit claim, no exit. cash≡0. The whole fund vocabulary (NAV / carry / IRR / cap-table / exit / dividend) is UNREPRESENTABLE (nusa :psychoactive / tazuna :weaponizable / kamado :fossil-virgin-crude pattern). Sustenance flows DOWN the existing in-kind rails (commons housing / mitsuho food / hikari energy / Murakumo compute / okaimono tooling / iyashi·hagukumi·kokoro care); the maintainer's irreducible external fiat need is routed ONLY as MEMBER-PRINCIPAL 0% liquidity via warifu — 扶持 never holds, lends, or pays cash (§1.3 holds without amendment). A horizontal control-plane sitting ON TOP of the Public Fund + Displacement Dividend + Basic-High-Income-in-kind machinery. ZERO invariant amendments — it STRENGTHENS cash≡0 (ADR-2605301020), no-server-key (ADR-2605231525), payoff帰属=etzhayyim, and the non-profit/donation-only invariants. Per ADR-2606052300."}}
